<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idc41a35ec-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1991—<ref href="/us/pl/102/40">Pub. L. 102–40</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s4205">section 4205 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/102/83">Pub. L. 102–83</ref> substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator” in two places.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1988—<ref href="/us/pl/100/322">Pub. L. 100–322</ref> inserted “or other interest-bearing accounts” after “checking accounts”.</p>
